{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/sourceref\/setcallback(func:data:notify:)"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/SourceRef\/setCallback(func:data:notify:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the callback function for a source. The callback for a source is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"called from the source’s dispatch function.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"setCallback","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"GSourceFunc","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GSourceFunc"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"data","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gpointer","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gpointer"},{"text":"? = nil, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"notify"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@GDestroyNotify","text":"GDestroyNotify"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil)"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The exact type of ","type":"text"},{"code":"func","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" depends on the type of source; ie. you","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"should not count on ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"func"},{"type":"text","text":" being called with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"data"},{"text":" as its first","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"parameter. Cast ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"func"},{"text":" with [func","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.SOURCE_FUNC"},{"type":"text","text":"] to avoid warnings ab